<paragraph blockId="3.[188,1398,508,576]" pageId="3" pageNumber="144">
This first record of 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Gravenhorst" baseAuthorityYear="1806" box="[413,539,508,535]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Quedius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="144" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="tenellus">
<emphasis box="[413,539,508,535]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="144">Q. tenellus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from Middle Asia is not unexpected because it had already been recorded from 
<collectingRegion box="[251,310,549,575]" country="Russia" name="Altay" pageId="3" pageNumber="144">Altai</collectingRegion>
Mountains in 
<collectingCountry box="[480,558,549,575]" name="Russia" pageId="3" pageNumber="144">Russia</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Salnitska M. &amp; Solodovnikov A." box="[573,952,549,575]" pageId="3" pageNumber="144" pagination="1 - 100" refId="ref9088" refString="Salnitska M. &amp; Solodovnikov A. 2019 Rove beetles of the genus Quedius (Coleoptera, Staphylinidae) of Russia: a key to species and annotated catalogue. ZooKeys 847: 1 - 100. https: // doi. org / 10.3897 / zookeys. 847.34049" type="journal article" year="2019">Salnitska &amp; Solodovnikov 2019</bibRefCitation>
) and 
<collectingCountry box="[1018,1132,549,575]" name="Mongolia" pageId="3" pageNumber="144">Mongolia</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Smetana A." box="[1147,1320,549,576]" pageId="3" pageNumber="144" pagination="21 - 28" refId="ref9200" refString="Smetana A. 1976. New species and remarks on Siberian Quedius (Coleoptera: Staphylinidae). Notulae Entomologicae 56: 21 - 28." type="journal article" year="1976">Smetana 1976</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
